Definition:
The intent of device is to be reused between both Questionniare and Questionnaire.item.
A device has details that consist of:
type : The device type (string)
reportField: field used for mapping data from the device report.
Questionnaire utilizes the type field to idenfity the type of device used within the Questionniare.
Questionniare.item utilizes reportField unless Questionnaire contains more then one device then Questionniare.item.device.detail must contain the device type
Condition(s):
ele-1:All FHIR elements must have a @value or children {hasValue() or (children().count() > id.count())}
ext-1:Must have either extensions or value[x], not both {extension.exists() != value.exists()}
